cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a new algorithm for continual learning in deep feedforward networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on deep feedforward networks and the experiments are conducted on image classification tasks, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories.
